 &lt;p&gt;day23 题目：&lt;span class=&#34;exturl&#34; data-url=&#34;aHR0cHM6Ly9sZWV0Y29kZS1jbi5jb20vcHJvYmxlbXMvc2h1LXp1LXpob25nLWNodS14aWFuLWNpLXNodS1jaGFvLWd1by15aS1iYW4tZGUtc2h1LXppLWxjb2Yv&#34;&gt;剑指 Offer 39. 数组中出现次数超过一半的数字&lt;/span&gt;、&lt;span class=&#34;exturl&#34; data-url=&#34;aHR0cHM6Ly9sZWV0Y29kZS1jbi5jb20vcHJvYmxlbXMvZ291LWppYW4tY2hlbmctamktc2h1LXp1LWxjb2Yv&#34;&gt;剑指 Offer 66. 构建乘积数组&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
